</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to cold SDS: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Deactivate all functions and set the printer in "cold" mode. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This test switches off all heaters in the system, and allows you to run several test without the usual error checks. 
</p><note id="GUID-477C4B9B-49D1-4BC1-8CD4-7B726455FE5C" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Switching to "cold" can only be done when the printer is not printing. 
