</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to warn SDS: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Activate all functions and set the printer in "warm" mode. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The warm SDS mode will start the printer in the usual operational state. 
